      aosDelay='200'
      text='See all Stars'
      block={false}
    />
    */
    }
  </Section>

  {/* Allstars */}
  <Section
    heading={{
      dataAos: 'fade-up',
      text: 'Elevating our Investment Strategy with our Allstars',
    }}
    paragraphs={[
      {
        dataAos: 'fade-left',
        dataAosDelay: '100',
        heading: 'Discover the Power of superangels',
        text: 'At superangels, we believe in the power of the swarm intelligence from the top performers of the business angel industry, uniting to become the force of superangels. Together, we  boast great capabilities to fuel investments in top tech companies.',
      },
      {
        dataAos: 'fade-right',
        dataAosDelay: '100',
        heading: 'Unparalleled Insights for Informed Investment Choices',
        text: 'Our approach is rooted in the expertise of tech industry experts, ensuring sharp investment decisions. Our allstar selection process included over 100 business angels and their investment portfolios, resulting in a selected group of 20 exceptional personalities. Each member of our network boasts specialized industry proficiency — whether it is AI/ML, Fintech/Crypto, Climate Tech, HR-Tech, Healthcare, and more. ',
      },
      {
        dataAos: 'fade-left',
        dataAosDelay: '100',
        heading: 'Collaboration for Pre-Seed/Seed Ventures',
        text: 'Our collaboration with these 20 allstars, embraces a "no questions asked" approach that eradicates "principal-agent" dynamics. This compromise can be observed when a group of investment managers in a typical fund campaigns for support for “their deals”. Our approach empowers the most independent investment decisions. The allstars invest their personal funds after a comprehensive due diligence, and we wholeheartedly endorse their expert decisions.',
      },
      {
        dataAos: 'fade-right',
        dataAosDelay: '100',
        heading: 'Strategically Mitigating Risk, Amplifying Returns',
        text: 'Our methodology effectively reduces risk and optimizes returns. By relying on the expertise of our allstars, we have crafted a strategy that leverages their deep industry insights and independent judgement.  We empower our proprietary allstar-investment team to make the most valuable investment decision, enabling an unusually large number of investments. Our goal is to get to 120-150 investments with our first fund. This high number of investments combined with the most valuable investment decision by our allstars mitigates risk very effectively. ',
      },
    ]}
    align='center'
    sectionId='team'
    sectionClass='section__6'
  >
    <div class='center'>
      <ul class='tag-list'>
        {
          tags.map((tag, index) => (
            <li class='tag-list__item'>
              <Tag title={tag} bordered={index !== tags.length - 1} />
            </li>
          ))
        }
      </ul>
      <p style='margin: 4rem 3rem 8rem'>
        We partner with these allstars and match their tickets for pre-seed/seed
        investments. Our model eliminates “principal-agent” issues by operating
        without employed managers to ensure independent investment decision.
        This strategy effectively minimizes risk and maximizes returns!
      </p>
    </div>
  </Section>
  <h1>Our Allstars</h1>
</Layout>

